# RAG Control Center - Comprehensive API Documentation

This document outlines the complete RESTful API architecture for the Dual-RAG backend. The backend is built using FastAPI and serves endpoints across four primary domains: **Health**, **Chat**, **Documents**, and **System & Logs**. 

All API routes (except the root health check) are prefixed with `/api/v1`.

